<HL>
   American Barrick Talking
   With Newmont on Merger
   ---
   Gold Miners Are Proposing
   To Swap Shares in Move
   Valued at $2.48 Billion
   ----
   By Larry M. Greenberg and Marj Charlier
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/29/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A3
</SO>
<CO>
   ABX HSM NEM T.ABX T.HSM
</CO>
